{"word":"G4717 - σταυρόω - stauróō - stow-ro'-o - Crucify","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σταυρόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>stauróō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>stow-ro'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Crucify"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சிலுவையில் அறை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to stake, drive down stakes"},{"paragraph":"2. to fortify with driven stakes"},{"paragraph":"3. to crucify"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4716 - σταυρός - staurós - stow-ros'/4716\">G4716</a>; to <i>impale</i> on the cross; figuratively to <i>extinguish</i> (<i>subdue</i>) passion or selfishness: - crucify."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}